         <h2>REST  behavior</h2>
         <p>Conformant systems must record <a href="{{site.data.fhir.path}}provenance.html">Provenance</a> records on all Create, Update and Delete actions on any resource other than Provenance or AuditEvent. Conformant systems must record <a href="{{site.data.fhir.path}}auditevent.html">AuditEvent</a> records on all Create, Update and Delete actions as well as all GET operations (read, search, etc.)</p>
